      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Turbo, featuring the legendary Mezger-designed 3.6L twin-turbocharged flat-six. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a crisp Getrag G96/50 six-speed manual transaxle and a factory-spec viscous-coupling AWD system. The coolant pipes have been proactively pinned, and the K16 turbochargers maintain peak boost pressure with zero shaft play. The exterior retains its factory-original paint with no measurable deviations, while the undercarriage remains concours-clean with no RMS or IMS weeping. A recent DME report confirms zero overrevs in higher ranges, ensuring this high-performance icon is as robust as it is pristine.",
