      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the term 'showroom condition.' This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage since day one, retaining its deep, lustrous factory finish which has been further protected by a professional ceramic coating. The exterior is laser-straight, completely free of stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in an untouched state; the premium leather upholstery is supple with no visible wear, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule with every service documented at the authorized dealership. From the pristine engine bay to the unmarked alloy wheels wrapped in fresh high-performance tires, every detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the highest standards for a discerning collector or enthusiast. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key example that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
